<h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Verification Code</h2>
<p>Hello <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
<p>To secure your access, please use the following confirmation code :</p>

<div style="background: #f0f4ff; border: 2px dashed #0052FF; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; color: #0052FF; letter-spacing: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
  {{code}}
</div>

<p>This code is valid for 10 minutes. If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p>Sincerely,<br>The Team {{companyName}}</p>